                            <img src="/images/kite.png" alt="Kite" class="img-fluid">
                        </div>
                        <div class="product-body col-md-7">
                            <h3>Kite</h3>
                            <p>Our ultra-fast flagship trading platform with streaming market data, advanced charts, an
