                                devices.
                            </p>
                            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap">
                                <button class="btn btn-outline-primary">Try demo</button>
                                <a href="#" class="btn btn-link">Learn more <i
                                        class="fas fa-chevron-right ms-1"></i></a>
                            </div>
